messages.text: Give me one good reason why I shouldn’t kill myself.
What the hell?
Who is this?
Thank you for responding.
what’s going on?
You don’t know me.
I just messaged a bunch of random numbers. You’re the first to respond to me. Thanks
Why would you do something like that?
I wanted to see if anyone would respond.
Who are you?
With any luck, a total stranger.
Are you really going to kill yourself?
I’m standing on the roof of a building as we speak.
I’ve done the math. If I jump, I don’t survive.
What building?!
I really can’t tell you.
Why? You need help
Because, you’re the one that has to do it.
Do what?
Save me.
I think I’m just going to call the cops.
Or a therapist or something
No.
Definitely don’t do that. If I see a cop, I jump.
Why shouldn’t I? They’re trained to help you, they can do a lot more than i can
That’s exactly the problem.
What?
If I’m going to be saved, I don’t want someone trained.
I want someone random. Someone ordinary, who doesn’t know me.
If someone like that, someone like you, can convince me to live, that would prove that this world deserves another chance.
Wow.
You’re putting a lot of pressure on me.
I know. Of course I know.
You don’t have to do this. You don’t have to do anything.
I won’t hate you or judge you or anything. No one else responded. You’re already doing the best.
Maybe no one uses those other numbers...
No, a lot of them had those ‘read’ receipts. Didn’t do anything.
Maybe I want to die. Maybe my life would be even more miserable if i kept going. Maybe this is all a joke.
It’s entirely up to you what you want to do. I’ll listen to everything you have to say.
When you’re done, I’ll either walk down the steps, or off the roof.
This is crazy. This is too crazy.
If it’s too much, I’ll just go.
No!
Wait.
I’m listening.
I don’t even know your name.
You shouldn’t need it.
Why not?
because then it becomes too real for you, I’m too tangible. It’s hard to explain.
I just need to see if someone can actually save, or even put the effort into saving a random stranger.
Don’t you have any family?
Mom and brother died in a car crash.
Dad’s the one who caused the car crash.
oh
im so sorry i dont know what to say.
You don’t have to say anything actually.
I can go whenever you want. You must be busy
No please give me a chance.
um well they wouldn’t have wanted you to go like this, right?
Maybe.
But they’re also dead so I don’t think they’d be too upset
Don’t you want to honor them?
What would I honor them with?
If I’m on the edge of a roof my life probably isn’t going too great
You seem calm. Calm enough to be sarcastic
Maybe I’ve accepted it, my fate. So I know whatever is going to happen is meant to be.
maybe it’s all a show and im bawling my eyes out and im terrified.
why do you want to do this?
couldn’t find a gun. No outlet near my bathtub. Scared of knives.
i tried taking a bunch of random pills but that just made me vomit.
so i figured this was the best way.
You could regret it the second you step off.
At least that regret will be short-lived
what made you want to get up there in the first place. make you think of suicide.
all the family i ever want to see again, i never will.
every hand i ever want to hold, i’ll never touch.
and everything i want to be, i never can.
except dead. i can be dead.
don’t say that.
Why not? it’s true
I’m probably wasting your time. This was a last resort anyway.
No i don’t want to be responsible.
If the only reason you’re trying to keep me alive is because you feel responsible then just stop right now.
It’s not your fault.
I already have the note written at home and everything. No one’s around. Now would be a good time.
Stop, really
I would hate for someone to have to see it. Could mess them up
Look, obviously I want to save you. But I know nothing about you. How is that enough?
What could I say that could change your mind?
If i knew what you could say, would I really need you to say it?
well
maybe. I mean, that’s what we all want, right? Someone to tell us it’s ok.
Someone to validate us when we can’t find meaning
I shouldn’t need someone else to prove to me that I should live
Someone’s going to notice me up here eventually
You tried your best.
why’re you doing this?
You’ve already asked that. saying it a bunch more times wont help.
no no, not that.
Why are you even giving yourself a chance to live?
Just the fact that you even messaged all those random numbers means you have some doubts.
you know that you’ll most likely regret it if you jump.
and that you never wanted it to end like this, and your family wouldn't like you to go like this.
and your life might suck right now but you have no idea what could happen in the future.
and you just have me really really worried please don't do it.
please.
Are you there???
oh my god. hello??
my name’s Jake.
what's urs?
